snippet.title: DRAGON BALL SUPER CARD GAME -Tutorial movie Vol.2-
snippet.description:
Want to learn how to play DRAGON BALL SUPER CARD GAME? Then look no further! This tutorial movie will teach you everything you need to know in order to play your first games of DBS card game. It's the new tutorial movie.
